Description: Minimal PDF page compositor for Linux
 Pertinax is a minimal PDF page compositor for Ubuntu LTS that allows
 users to organize PDF pages without modifying source files. It provides
 a GTK 4 graphical interface and command-line tool.
 .
 Features:
  - Open and import PDF files
  - Reorder and delete pages
  - Preview pages with zoom
  - Export to new PDF
  - Immutable source files (never modified)
 .
 This tool is focused on page organization only and does not provide
 text editing, annotations, or other PDF editing features.
